
 L T X                         set_stream                         L T X
 
 NAME
	set_stream - sets a clients stream list to the given streams.

 SYNOPSIS
	set_stream <client name> [<stream name>...]

	The command set_stream sets the given clients list based on 
	the stream list. Note that this will remove the current client 
	stream list and create a new one. The client name must be 
	currently active. To get a list of current clients, use the 
	command list_clients.

